data.description: Step into a home where quality craftsmanship and thoughtful design come together on a sprawling 4.62-acre lot. This residence promises not just a house, but a lifestyle of comfort and luxury. The home offers stunning southern views, making it a perfect sanctuary for those who appreciate nature and tranquility.  Inside, the home is a testament to fine living, featuring top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances and granite counters that elevate your culinary experience. One of the standout features of this property is the 3-car garage, providing ample space for your vehicles and additional storage. The home is designed for those who don't want to compromise on quality or space.
